      <subsection name="Examples" id="Examples">
        <p id="Example1-config">
          To configure the default check:
        </p>
        <source>
&lt;module name=&quot;Checker&quot;&gt;
  &lt;module name=&quot;TreeWalker&quot;&gt;
    &lt;module name=&quot;MethodCount&quot;/&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
        </source>

        <p id="Example2-config">
          To configure the check to allow no more than 30 methods per type declaration:
        </p>
        <source>
&lt;module name=&quot;Checker&quot;&gt;
  &lt;module name=&quot;TreeWalker&quot;&gt;
    &lt;module name=&quot;MethodCount&quot;&gt;
      &lt;property name=&quot;maxTotal&quot; value=&quot;30&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
        </source>

        <p id="Example3-config">
          To configure the check to allow no more than 10 public methods per
          type declaration, and 40 methods in total:
        </p>
        <source>
&lt;module name=&quot;Checker&quot;&gt;
  &lt;module name=&quot;TreeWalker&quot;&gt;
    &lt;module name=&quot;MethodCount&quot;&gt;
      &lt;property name=&quot;maxPublic&quot; value=&quot;10&quot;/&gt;
      &lt;property name=&quot;maxTotal&quot; value=&quot;40&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
        </source>

      </subsection>

